Package: ShinyFruit
Type: Package
Title: Batch Image Analysis GUI for Small Fruits
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Mason Chizk
Maintainer: Mason Chizk <tmchizk@uark.edu>
Description: This package uses C++ image processing methods contained in the 
    magick and imager packages combined with a shiny GUI to simplify image
    processing and data collection in small fruit crops like blackberry.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
